Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://bodz.net/

Package: git-union
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, git, python3
Description: merge multiple git repositories into one monorepo
 git-union creates a new git repository and replays commits from multiple
 source repositories, placing each source under its own subdirectory.
 It supports optional cross-repository commit interleaving by author time
 while preserving per-repository commit order.
